project.name: Freecell IPC2
project.description: This model is based on the Freecell domain from IPC-2 (2000), Originally written by Nolan Andres and Robert HillHouse. Freecell is a solitaire card game that comes with Microsoft Windows.

operator.name: move
operator.description: Move card between columns. Two versions dependent on whether or not we generate a new stack.
operator.constraints:
pre: card.clear = true and newcard.clear = true and card.canstack = newcard and card.on = oldcard
post: card.on = newcard and oldcard.clear = true and newcard.clear = false

operator.name: moveb
operator.description: Move card between columns. Two versions dependent on whether or not we generate a new stack.
operator.constraints:
pre: card.clear = true and card.bottomcol = true and newcard.clear = true and card.canstack = newcard and cols.colspace = true and ncols.successor = cols
post: card.on = newcard and ncols.colspace = true and card.bottomcol = false and newcard.clear = false and cols.colspace = false

operator.name: sendtofree
operator.description: Send a card to a freecell. Two versions dependent on whether or not we generate a new stack.
operator.constraints:
pre: card.clear = true and card.on = oldcard and cells.cellspace = true and cells.successor = ncells
post: card.incell = true and oldcard.clear = true and ncells.cellspace and card.on = null and card.clear = false and cells.cellspace = false

operator.name: sendtofreeb
operator.description: Send a card to a freecell. Two versions dependent on whether or not we generate a new stack.
operator.constraints:
pre: card.clear = true and card.bottomcol = true and cells.cellspace = true and cells.successor = ncells and cols.colspace = true and ncols.successor = cols
post: card.incell = true and ncols.colspace = true and ncells.cellspace = true and card.bottomcol = false and card.clear = false and cols.colspace = false and cells.cellspace = false

operator.name: sendtonewcol
operator.description: Send a card a new column
operator.constraints:
pre: card.clear = true and cols.colspace = true and cols.successor = ncols and card.on = oldcard
post: card.bottomcol = true and oldcard.clear = true and ncols.colspace = true and card.on = null and cols.colspace = false

operator.name: sendtohome
operator.constraints:
pre: card.clear = true and card.on = oldcard and homecard.home = true and card.suit = suitt and homecard.suit = suitt and card.value = vcard and homecard.value = vhomecard and vcard.successor = vhomecard
post: card.home = true and oldcard.clear = true and card.on = null and homecard.home = false and card.clear = false

operator.name: sendtohomeb
operator.constraints:
pre: card.clear = true and card.bottomcol = true and homecard.home = true and card.suit = suitt and homecard.suit = suitt and card.value = vcard and homecard.value = vhomecard and vcard.successor = vhomecard and cols.colspace = true and ncols.successor = cols
post: card.home = true and ncols.colspace = true and homecard.home = false and card.clear = false and card.bottomcol = false and cols.colspace = false

operator.name: homefromfreecell
operator.constraints:
pre: card.incell = true and homecard.home = true and card.suit = suitt and homecard.suit = suitt and card.value = vcard and homecard.value = vhomecard and vcard.successor = vhomecard and cells.cellspace = true and ncells.successor = cells
post: card.home = true and ncells.cellspace = true and card.incell = false and cells.cellspace = false and homecard.home = false

operator.name: colfromfreecell
operator.constraints:
pre: card.incell = true and newcard.clear = true and card.canstack = newcard and cells.cellspace = true and ncells.successor = cells
post: ncells.cellspace = true and card.clear = true and card.on = newcard and card.incell = false and cells.cellspace = false and newcard.clear = false

operator.name: newcolfromfreecell
operator.constraints:
pre: card.incell = true and cols.colspace = true and cells.cellspace = true and cols.successor = ncols and ncells.successor = cells
post: card.bottomcol = true and card.clear = true and ncols.colspace = true and ncells.cellspace = true and card.incell = false and cols.colspace = false and cells.cellspace = false
